skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: personal guess who
des: With this skill, you will be able to to play Guess Who with Alexa based on the category of animals. The rules for Guess Who is pretty basic and easy to learn. Alexa will described to you 2-3 facts/hints about this animal and all you have to do is guess what animal it is.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
